        documents of the traveler

        Parameters:
        number - The document number (shown on the document) . E.g. QFU514563221J
        issuanceDate - Date at which the document has been issued.
        expiryDate - Date after which the document is not valid anymore.
        issuanceCountry - ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 of the country that issued the document
        issuanceLocation - A more precise information concerning the place where the document has been issued, when available. It may be a country, a state, a city or any other type of location. e.g. New-York
        nationality - ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 of the nationality appearing on the document
        birthPlace - Birth place as indicated on the document
        documentType -
        validityCountry - ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 of the country where the document is valid
        birthCountry - ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 of the country of birth
        holder - boolean to specify if the traveler is the holder of the document
